para_trans: Regarding in-principle administrative approval to the budget for construction of Government Hostel for Backward Classes Girls, Mahadevpura, T.G. Wardha.
Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance
Government Decision No: BCH-2025 / Q.94 / Constructions
Madam Kama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Reference: - Department of Social Justice and Special Assistance, Government Decision No. BCH-2025 / Q.94 / Constructions,

The Government Hostel for Backward Classes Girls, Mahadevpura, T.G. Wardha under Social Justice and Special Assistance Department has been constructed at a cost of Rs. 2445.77 Attention / - Government decision regarding construction budget of such amount. Administrative approval has been granted in principle subject to the conditions prescribed under 04.11.2025; the Government decision includes condition number (t) as follows: -
The operational mechanism for the proposed construction will be the Maharashtra-State Infrastructure Development Corporation (MSIDC), Mumbai.
(2) The other provisions of the Government Decision shall remain in force.
The Government Correctional Certificate is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
